msContents.summary: Contains the only extant copy of al-Māturīdī's Kitāb al-tawḥīd. This treatise discusses the opinions of different religious groups -both Muslim and non-Muslim- on a variety of theological issues, with especial attention to the polemics concerning the attributes of God.

name.persName: Māturīdī, Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad, d. 944 or 5
